  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort rooms</strong> are about 15-18m² and are housed in the new wing and feature parquet flooring, classic furniture, marble bathroom and double or twin beds. HD TV, WiFi, air conditioning and minibar. These rooms sleep two people.</p>
<p><strong>Superior rooms </strong>are about 20-22m² with high ceilings and large windows. The rooms fully refurbished and are located in the 19<sup>th</sup> Century Villa.</p>
<p><strong>Elegance rooms </strong>are about 18 m² and housed in the modern wing of the building. They have fantastic views across the Grotta Gusti Park gardens.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe rooms</strong> are about 22m² and are located in the old villa, with views over the gardens. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are about 40 - 44m² and are located in the modern wing of the resort. These rooms have views of the mountains or the beautiful part. They sleep up to three people. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms </strong>are about 30 - 44m². These two interconnecting rooms are in the modern wing with views over the gardens, allowing families to spend relaxing time together in this beautiful location. These rooms sleep up to four people. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
